WebPage.name: breadcrumb
WebPage.desc: A set of links that can help a user understand and navigate a website hierarchy.

WebPage.name: significantLink
WebPage.desc: One of the more significant URLs on the page. Typically, these are the non-navigation links that are clicked on the most.

WebPage.name: relatedLink
WebPage.desc: A link related to this web page, for example to other related web pages.

WebPage.name: lastReviewed
WebPage.desc: Date on which the content on this web page was last reviewed for accuracy and/or completeness.

WebPage.name: mainContentOfPage
WebPage.desc: Indicates if this web page element is the main subject of the page.

WebPage.name: reviewedBy
WebPage.desc: People or organizations that have reviewed the content on this web page for accuracy and/or completeness.

WebPage.name: primaryImageOfPage
WebPage.desc: Indicates the main image on the page.

WebPage.name: significantLinks
WebPage.desc: The most significant URLs on the page. Typically, these are the non-navigation links that are clicked on the most.

WebPage.name: specialty
WebPage.desc: One of the domain specialities to which this web page's content applies.
